metadata.name: Hypnotize with the Lies
metadata.description: Absolutely incredible, how easy is it to manipulate people.  To show them things on TV, show fabricated facts AND THEY BELIEVE IT. It is hard for me to wrap my head around this thing that society as a whole doesn't have a critical thinking. And that what has inspired me to create this artwork. A nonsense thing that is delivered to people under a cover of bright and happy lies is something that everyone will believe. Insanity.
